If your self-hosted strategy includes any of the following...

- Open ports on your server for the services you run
- SSL Encryption using LetsEncrypt
- DNS records pointing directly to your server's IPv4/IPv6 address

Your self-hosting strategy is wrong! Not only is it wrong, your host might as well
have a target painted on it. 1
